
Overview of noun advertising

The noun advertising has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                    
1. (7) ad, advertisement, advertizement, advertising, advertizing, advert -- (a public promotion of some product or service)
2. (6) advertising, publicizing -- (the business of drawing public attention to goods and services)

Overview of verb advertise

The verb advertise has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (7) advertise, publicize, advertize, publicise -- (call attention to; "Please don't advertise the fact that he has AIDS")
2. advertise, advertize, promote, push -- (make publicity for; try to sell (a product); "The salesman is aggressively pushing the new computer model"; "The company is heavily advertizing their new laptops")
